{"tid":351721,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"郭文貴爆馬英九遭中共控制 才抓陳水扁入獄 願意來台灣法院作證人或出示證據","createTime":"2017-08-08T09:36:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-15T04:47:34.000Z","uid":35790,"like":45,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cdff1ec9e6378d669f272b26509c3785f3fc8673","tid":351721,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T09:36:13.000Z","msg":"【傻眼片】郭文貴爆馬英九遭控制　才抓陳水扁入獄<br />\n流亡海外的中國富豪郭文貴昨晚在社群網站稱，中國在台灣佈下天兵天將，也無法撼動陳水扁。郭文貴又說，馬英九上台後，中國高官對於控制他深感信心，並稱他會重新定義「九二共識」，響應中國的「大蘿蔔政策」，兩岸經濟會更加緊密，郭又引述高官稱「馬英九一定會抓住陳水扁，我們已經給他要求了，他一定會抓住」。<br />\n<br />\n另名高官說「已經控制馬英九生活多年，他不敢說啥，我們想讓他幹嘛就讓他幹嘛&hellip;他的兩個女兒也在我們視線範圍內」。他又續稱能這樣控制馬英九，是因為有致命之招，讓馬不得不就範。郭文貴爆馬英九受中共控制多年　馬辦駁斥：不隨腦補起舞<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n郭文貴說，這些在日後都得到證實，馬英九也一反以往溫和風格，激進地把陳水扁送入監獄。郭文貴說，歡迎馬英九到美國起訴他，也願意來台灣到法院作證人或出示證據，「文貴與馬先生、台灣各高官、企業家無冤無仇，只是為了台灣人民的未來與尊嚴而已！」郭文貴描述中共對台灣、香港和澳門的「藍金黃計畫」，以此對港、澳、台官員和商人進行控制，並且已實施一、二十年。藍色是網路控制，透過收買各種媒體平台，進而到達全面的洗腦計畫；金色就是使用金錢收買，利用非法利益收買台商，台商到台灣後繼續收買相關人士；黃色就是使用性賄絡，利用賭博、色情等行業，掌握台灣高官的賭博、色情證據，對其進行敲詐，「很多國民黨高官換身分，到澳門賭博嫖娼亂淫」。（大陸中心／綜合外電報導）臉書上最有趣國際新聞，都在蘋果繞著地球爆發稿 14：59<br />\n更新 16：55<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170808/1177902\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Finternational%2F20170808%2F1177902&d=HV1dzBfdtOGeWDRNYTgTm8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=2413f997\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170808/1177902</a>"},{"pid":"ccde44692af6266c78fe0a93497b89b07c3ba51f","tid":351721,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T09:36:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab339b4133ee7e8ae4f9a7e083f28a131acf42af","tid":351721,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T09:39:55.000Z","msg":"九哥自稱係炎黃子孫<br />\n中華民族 梗係愛中國"},{"pid":"f0ec0c392b72858aca8afb74de9b9e9418c2e832","tid":351721,"uid":24140,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T09:48:15.000Z","msg":"一早就話陳水扁唔係衰貪污<br />\n國民黨班死老野 國公教 貪貪埋埋多過佢過百倍<br />\n<br />\n佢主要想研制核彈，比支那同美國整死佢"},{"pid":"8b5f727ea51f64c17f67141f7dfc7505429b349b","tid":351721,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T09:54:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://cc.tvbs.com.tw/news2.0/img/200602/28/lili-20060228175659.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcc.tvbs.com.tw%2Fnews2.0%2Fimg%2F200602%2F28%2Flili-20060228175659.jpg&h=b766e5be&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4006777768865a05aad82cddfb37a2ea15c07916","tid":351721,"uid":100986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T09:58:24.000Z","msg":"發達啦巴打通過<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"204d27490ec529c9e3daf29edc6864976b2a185a","tid":351721,"uid":100986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T09:58:46.000Z","msg":"發達啦巴打<strong>講過</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb24623cfb2e0bc9977bb9b0c889af6cbb278c5e","tid":351721,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T10:03:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a7f37f08c01d89af20560861a1cd81d102b5eb2","tid":351721,"uid":100986,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T10:11:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>發達啦巴打<strong>講過</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n發達啦巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7a4db7411de15e36f634f2565ad2e498c98e4cf","tid":351721,"uid":105261,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T12:31:16.000Z","msg":"郭文貴爆料的內容有關台灣的大約如下: <br />\n<br />\n1.中共布下天羅地網對付陳水扁，但沒有成功 <br />\n<br />\n2.連戰跟陳水扁選的那次，中共看好連戰獲勝 <br />\n<br />\n3.中共控制馬英九非常徹底，中共握有對馬英九一擊必殺的殺手鐧 <br />\n包括馬英九的兩個女兒也是控制之下 <br />\n<br />\n4.中共要求馬英九主要有三件事: <br />\n1.速關陳水扁 2.定義九二共識 3.讓台灣和中國經濟結合 <br />\n<br />\n5.中共對付台灣香港的計畫，總結三個字「藍金黃」 <br />\n計畫已實施一二十年，最近幾年速度加劇 <br />\n藍: 網路侵入，不是只有網路而已，而是包括各種媒體民調傳播平台 <br />\n簡單來說就是中共透過各種手段控制收買台港各種傳播平台 <br />\n進而到達對台灣香港的全面洗腦計畫 <br />\n金: 簡單說就是金錢收買，給台商不法利益來收買 <br />\n然後這些台商回台之後，透過這些台商繼續收買相關人士 <br />\n黃: 利用賭博色情行業，掌握台灣高官的賭博色情的證據 <br />\n郭文貴說他有這些人的證據視頻 <br />\n<br />\n6.某位大名鼎鼎的台商收了中共很大的好處，還睡了兩位女明星 <br />\n<br />\nPTT COPY"},{"pid":"7a2709079e203493f81ce98b3dddd041f310ef1b","tid":351721,"uid":34098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T13:56:45.000Z","msg":"湯渣都係俾人話叫雞俾人影，之後搞到現在咁"},{"pid":"e0dbb25b6ab0b49a49b344765d8e3838b34687cf","tid":351721,"uid":34098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T13:58:48.000Z","msg":"搞死高登，同埋連登背後老闆都好似紅底"},{"pid":"79baa505805e0d27c591c42de7ca716124d8b8ba","tid":351721,"uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T14:02:29.000Z","msg":"共產黨有冇咁神通廣大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aeaebf7ae46d753bfde8b295fec6d06058b47590","tid":351721,"uid":30169,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T14:08:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>共產黨有冇咁神通廣大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你啱啱出世？"},{"pid":"0bf286afe24c37e6b246a37029ad06a17a1e6e48","tid":351721,"uid":53705,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T14:30:03.000Z","msg":"每次見到郭文貴, 我都想問<br />\n<br />\n飯冰冰 條片呢?? 幾時找數呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f463e02d2ab0c3eee8c0f2e8c0b597b49469768f","tid":351721,"uid":36820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T14:33:13.000Z","msg":"片呢屌"},{"pid":"254fcfba12cdb237ce564e6fbb1c347167c197e5","tid":351721,"uid":54876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T14:35:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>共產黨有冇咁神通廣大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無話神通廣大，只係對支那人劣根性有充分研究。<br />\n<br />\n香港台灣班人又戒唔甩支那惡習"},{"pid":"b4504bae95c93f42f6c28ed5fd8b4d80ccbc6d49","tid":351721,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T14:54:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>共產黨有冇咁神通廣大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無話神通廣大，只係對支那人劣根性有充分研究。<br />\n<br />\n香港台灣班人又戒唔甩支那惡習</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當年中共比國民黨圍剿完, 要「長征」(其實係走佬) 去延安, 人數得番唔夠兩萬人<br />\n但中共一樣有能力派間諜 滲透國民黨<br />\n更何況今時今日, 中共佔據成個大陸<br />\n<br />\n上帝創造中共, 就係專門搞鳩國民黨"},{"pid":"894881da8bd2be7de6605055e56cbdb0daf6bc49","tid":351721,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T14:56:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MkPoXvENxr8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DMkPoXvENxr8&d=HV1dzBfdtOGeWDRNYTgTm8PrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=d18b9154\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=MkPoXvENxr8</a>"},{"pid":"d7bcb03757960d0b445857993f05190cc05df848","tid":351721,"uid":92072,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T15:09:13.000Z","msg":"馬英九任內戰績:<br />\n服貿<br />\n拉陳水扁<br />\n習馬會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家國民黨仲有習洪會 所以國民黨就算9數啦<br />\n<br />\n唔怪知當年陳水扁要係卸任之前個刻上飛機走佬 又唔怪知馬英九做咁多野阻住陳水扁去機場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5009a80f64193c26472b8182ef99e871cacd1b5","tid":351721,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T15:25:59.000Z","msg":"馬英九真係好撚賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"135495946bdd313c387ad478f2d5bc1bceb144a8","tid":351721,"uid":4783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T16:46:34.000Z","msg":"拉陳水扁就擺到明有hidden agenda啦<br />\n講國務機要費案 其實馬狗自己都係咁claim <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal